4
00:00:49,666 --> 00:00:53,750
<i>You can't help</i>
<i>but clench your teeth</i>

5
00:00:53,833 --> 00:00:57,500
<i>As your heart starts</i>
<i>to tremble from the heat</i>

6
00:00:57,583 --> 00:01:03,125
<i>Now stop it</i>
<i>It'll only bring destruction</i>

7
00:01:03,208 --> 00:01:07,833
<i>Let's do it!</i>
<i>I killed an angel</i>

8
00:01:07,916 --> 00:01:12,166
<i>The time has come</i>
<i>to stand and be strong</i>

9
00:01:12,250 --> 00:01:16,500
<i>It's a sad history</i>
<i>hidden in a big story</i>

10
00:01:16,583 --> 00:01:19,250
<i>That is the mystery</i>

11
00:01:19,333 --> 00:01:23,208
<i>There's no way now of knowin'</i>

12
00:01:23,291 --> 00:01:27,166
<i>Knowin' about what</i>
<i>tomorrow holds for me</i>

13
00:01:27,250 --> 00:01:32,750
<i>So I just keep moving on</i>
<i>Living till the moment's gone</i>

14
00:01:32,833 --> 00:01:36,583
<i>Forever just me</i>
<i>My mission</i>

15
00:01:56,166 --> 00:01:57,500
Man this job is boring.

16
00:01:57,583 --> 00:02:01,500
Tell me about it. Us
newbies get the crap work.

17
00:02:01,583 --> 00:02:02,916
I told my folks
I would make it big

18
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:05,041
when I left home,
and now I'm stuck out here

19
00:02:05,125 --> 00:02:06,833
and haven't even shot my weapon.

20
00:02:13,375 --> 00:02:14,458
What's up?

21
00:02:14,541 --> 00:02:16,416
I think I saw a kid.

22
00:02:16,500 --> 00:02:18,708
A kid? Are you sure about that?

23
00:02:18,791 --> 00:02:19,958
We're way far out.

24
00:02:20,041 --> 00:02:21,916
This is the last place
I'd expect to see a kid.

25
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:23,583
No man, I'm serious.

26
00:02:24,291 --> 00:02:25,583
Check it out.

27
00:02:26,333 --> 00:02:28,083
See! There it was again!

28
00:02:28,708 --> 00:02:29,958
Hold up!

29
00:02:30,041 --> 00:02:32,083
You're not supposed
to leave your post!

30
00:02:32,958 --> 00:02:34,208
Idiot.

31
00:02:57,541 --> 00:02:59,458
How much longer
do we have to wait?

32
00:02:59,541 --> 00:03:00,125
Easy.

33
00:03:00,208 --> 00:03:01,333
Have some patience.

34
00:03:01,416 --> 00:03:02,833
No, kidding.

35
00:03:02,916 --> 00:03:04,500
By the time the
sun rises tomorrow

36
00:03:04,583 --> 00:03:05,375
we'll have more money

37
00:03:05,458 --> 00:03:07,291
than we'll know what to do with.

38
00:03:09,125 --> 00:03:10,625
What's going on?!

39
00:03:10,708 --> 00:03:12,250
Oh... Sorry...

40
00:03:12,333 --> 00:03:14,583
Did we wake you Mr. Shimada?

41
00:03:15,375 --> 00:03:18,500
Isn't it about time
you guys changed guards?

42
00:03:18,583 --> 00:03:19,958
Right. We lost track of time.

43
00:03:20,041 --> 00:03:21,291
We'll get on that right away.

44
00:03:21,375 --> 00:03:23,666
Come on guys, let's punch
it up a bit, let's move!

45
00:03:23,750 --> 00:03:25,375
I'm moving, I'm moving.

46
00:03:26,125 --> 00:03:28,166
So, why isn't
she eating anything?

47
00:03:28,250 --> 00:03:30,125
Don't know. She
won't even look at it.

48
00:03:30,208 --> 00:03:31,541
We warmed it up and everything.

49
00:03:31,625 --> 00:03:34,000
I put the mask back on
her just to keep her quiet.

50
00:03:34,083 --> 00:03:35,083
Guess she's not a big fan

51
00:03:35,166 --> 00:03:37,375
of cookies, butter,
and dog food.

52
00:03:41,666 --> 00:03:44,291
Well, she can
starve for all I care.

53
00:03:44,375 --> 00:03:46,166
If she continues to
refuse I could always

54
00:03:46,250 --> 00:03:47,666
shove the food down her throat.

55
00:03:47,750 --> 00:03:49,041
Just leave her be.

56
00:03:49,125 --> 00:03:50,458
Come morning when
our client arrives

57
00:03:50,541 --> 00:03:53,083
this little babysitting
job will be over.

58
00:03:54,166 --> 00:03:55,166
This brat is gonna make us

59
00:03:55,250 --> 00:03:56,958
some serious money ain't she?

60
00:03:57,041 --> 00:03:58,208
I figure each
of us will get more

61
